    • org.apache.flink.api.java.utils.Option

public class Option

      • alt

        public Option alt(String shortName)
        Define an alternative / short name of the parameter. Only one alternative per parameter is allowed.
        参数:
        shortName - - short version of the parameter name
        返回:
        the updated Option

      • type

        public Option type(OptionType type)
        Define the type of the Option.
        参数:
        type - - the type which the the value of the Option can be casted to.
        返回:
        the updated Option

      • defaultValue

        public Option defaultValue(String defaultValue)
                    throws RequiredParametersException
        Define a default value for the option. Throws an exception if the list of possible values for the parameter is not empty and the default value passed is not in the list.
        参数:
        defaultValue - - the default value
        返回:
        the updated Option
        抛出:
        RequiredParametersException

      • choices

        public Option choices(String... choices)
               throws RequiredParametersException
        Restrict the list of possible values of the parameter.
        参数:
        choices - - the allowed values of the parameter.
        返回:
        the updated Option
        抛出:
        RequiredParametersException

        the updated Option
